Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text:
Located in the heart of Rochester’s southeast submarket on the Route 96
office corridor with superior access to I-490 and I-90 (New York State Thruway).

Nearby area amenities include restaurants, banks and Eastview Mall, the region’s premier shopping mall featuring over 180 stores including 30 specialty shops which are unique to the market.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Greater Rochester Area’s premier office park offering 516,000 square feet of Class A office space. On-site accommodations available at Woodcliff Hotel & Spa which features a conference center with 6,000 SF of meeting space accommodating up to 200 people, 236 guest rooms, indoor and outdoor pool, Horizons Restaurant and Lounge, Spa Elan, tennis and golf.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Woodcliff Office Park is one of the Greater Rochester Area’s premier office environments, offering numerous on-site amenities and a convenient location near I-490 at the interchange with Interstate-90 (the New York State Thruway Exit 45) providing superior access to the Rochester Market as well as the Western New York and Finger Lakes Regions.
